 hand, but you get good at it surprisingly fast.\n\nWill you reach the top?", "short_description": "Jetbounce is a Collect-a-Thon Platformer where you collect gems and explore large open worlds.\n\nAll hand crafted levels and obstacles, designed for multiple paths.\nYou are rewarded for your exploration and boldness.\n\nIntuitive controls: press a button to activate your Jetpack, release it to jump and fly at the direction you're aiming.\n\nWill you reach the top?"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wv8p_ZmThhlgjrFFQX-9JzDVbA1FcMdDUYqefYzExHs", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Kastel Software", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://discord.gg/eMKhfBmR8E", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ADVENTURE", "EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "251431297138265"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 5, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1627668954739783"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "533058315214904"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "427180075624529"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1137727443698397"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "350469833694202"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1627668954739783"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1722558803, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1627668954739783"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [